context_messages.content:
QuestItemUI you can change to some model you have in world that won't have any code in it.
or if using the block

can add this toggle off base cube model.  But if you intend to do that, might as well just make it a tree/desk/random world prop.

```
app.configure([
  {
    key: 'visibility',
    type: 'switch',
    label: 'Block Visibility',
    hint: 'Whether the block is visible in the world',
    options: [
      { label: 'Visible', value: 'visible', hint: 'Block is visible' },
      { label: 'Invisible', value: 'invisible', hint: 'Block is hidden' }
    ],
    initial: 'visible'
  }
])


const block = app.get('Block')

if (props.visibility === 'invisible') {
  block.active = false;
} 

```

